<span class="toggle-direction"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></span>
</div>

<div class="accordion-description">
<p>To receive a bonus, log in to your account, open the "Bonus" page and click "receive bonus." You can receive this type of bonus an unlimited number of times per day. The time for receiving bonus depends on the chosen tariff plan</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="accordion-box">

<div class="accordion-header">
